{"tid":213973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[清倉賣野] 大量中式廚/餐具枱櫈酒杯","createTime":"2017-04-23T13:00:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T13:51:41.000Z","uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29f5aec507fc9e9382799df2d8700a51765230a6","tid":213973,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"大家好 今日我係黎散貨<br />\n同經理執倉 太多野唔要<br />\n我地係睇過來貨價再減先賣出黎<br />\n有杯有櫈有碟 乜鳩都有<br />\n我地唔想賣比夜冷鋪又唔想掉<br />\n希望有巴打有公司可以要左佢 好多都好新<br />\n希望大家幫下手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲圖用手機up上黎 點轉佢都係頭已側 <br />\n不便之處 敬請原諒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/d4pf2r1m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fd4pf2r1m&h=bfcf09be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左邊 180$兩張 中間250一張 右邊300一張<br />\n如果你唔洗睇貨 櫈可以過數比埋運費 <br />\n我係倉叫車 送到你樓下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ft7j8b2p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fft7j8b2p&h=d6306419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/b7noi48l\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fb7noi48l&h=8a7fab1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h0c8k3qy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh0c8k3qy&h=9c1e496f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大燉盅 100蚊1個 小燉盅 70蚊1個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/n0i9cte4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fn0i9cte4&h=f083cc3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n三腳鼎無蓋 15蚊3個 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g1fw3hno\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg1fw3hno&h=bbbf146d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金屬盤 10蚊1隻 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vl0913fx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvl0913fx&h=a91a2747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅a827膠西 25蚊1個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/szd2o01y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fszd2o01y&h=47d8e27c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意大利直刀切肉機 4500蚊<br />\n絞肉機 3000蚊<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/enxk2fzs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fenxk2fzs&h=f7087e4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攪餡機 3200蚊<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nbsi5hf0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnbsi5hf0&h=dd79528b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣磨豆機 1800蚊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pc0fdyi5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpc0fdyi5&h=08a2afc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀角大碟 30蚊隻 大量<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/j0ta78rh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fj0ta78rh&h=670d0ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒸籠 35蚊一條 一條7個 共2條<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0gzvexou\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0gzvexou&h=9979db63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n石鍋  80蚊一個<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/y3g14frw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fy3g14frw&h=7453aeb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冰箱 400蚊<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hdkul6ie\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhdkul6ie&h=fa948120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鐵枱 100蚊一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2hfdw6yj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2hfdw6yj&h=66bd7d0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kayuwfxn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkayuwfxn&h=e4bfbf62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微波爐 暖風機 各120蚊 <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zujpbv2t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzujpbv2t&h=63f8b3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n輪椅上落樓梯機 30000蚊 送輪椅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/40ndrcij\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F40ndrcij&h=f188f28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/spit8kxl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fspit8kxl&h=fc58ec10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gaxm04l1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgaxm04l1&h=9064dfc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lravx0q8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flravx0q8&h=5763de8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jq4nrgi0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjq4nrgi0&h=e3a512c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dsihc1tv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdsihc1tv&h=cd256e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/76w1obhu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F76w1obhu&h=809ead96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yjaor5wk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyjaor5wk&h=7d0ac608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cyfw7ez5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcyfw7ez5&h=ff0ac9f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nshooter杯 260蚊12隻       martini杯 60蚊3隻<br />\n香檳杯 80蚊4隻  兩用香檳或白酒杯 120蚊6隻 共2盒<br />\n地杯 150蚊9隻      有盒既110蚊6隻<br />\n大直身杯     15蚊隻有38隻       有盒120蚊6隻<br />\n細直身杯  120蚊6隻 <br />\n不同size水晶紅酒杯  140蚊7隻    特大120蚊6隻<br />\n水晶rock杯    120蚊6隻有5盒"},{"pid":"0c18147b1d4ca63ade189be6890ce4a2c6262730","tid":213973,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:02:30.000Z","msg":"留個名先"},{"pid":"903710519febe211f04d3f4f6f5a8275c9da894e","tid":213973,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dis